name: THENODE
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
The Node improves the problems of existing mining methods by combining Ethereum chain and Master Node chain via THENODE DUAL CORE. Coins mined through node operation can be used in incubating investments and own Dapps,
and the amount of circulation increased due to mining is controlled by market logic by burning of used coins via incubating investments.
